# Talovka (selo), Republic of Buryatia

}}
Talovka () is a rural locality (a selo) in Pribaykalsky District, Republic of Buryatia, Russia. The population was 161 as of 2010. There are 6 streets.
Geography
Talovka is located 44&nbsp;km southwest of Turuntayevo (the district's administrative centre) by road. Yugovo is the nearest rural locality.
